import React from "react";

import Item from "../Components/genericItemComponent";

                borderColor: 'grey.500',

                margin: 'auto',
                padding: '1rem',
                borderRadius:"12px"
            }}>
                <Typography 
                variant="h4"
                align="center"
                gutterBottom>
                    Welcome to Tinder Paws!
                </Typography>

                <Typography
                ariant="body1"
                align="center">
                    {createIntro(text)}
                </Typography>
            </Box>
            {/* <Stack 
            spacing={4}

                <Item>Start application and visit your match</Item>
                <Item>Adopt and Pick Up</Item>
                <Item>Enjoy life with your companion</Item>
            </Stack> */}
            <Stack
            alignItems="center"
            justifyContent="space-evenly">
                {createFlowchartItems(sequence)}
                {/* <ListItem sx={{ width:"40%", border: 1, borderRadius:"12px", borderColor:"grey.500",padding:"0%", margin:"3% 3%"}}>
                    <ListItemText sx={{textAlign:"center", padding:"0%"}}>Create an account</ListItemText>
                </ListItem>
                <ListItem sx={{margin:"auto", width:"40%", border: 1, borderRadius:"12px", borderColor:"grey.500",padding:"0%"}}>
                    <ListItemText sx={{textAlign:"center", padding:"0%"}}>Look through available animals</ListItemText>
                </ListItem>
                <ListItem sx={{margin:"auto", width:"40%", border: 1, borderRadius:"12px", borderColor:"grey.500",padding:"0%"}}>
                    <ListItemText sx={{textAlign:"center", padding:"0%"}}>Match with one of the animals</ListItemText>
                </ListItem>
                <ListItem sx={{margin:"auto", width:"40%", border: 1, borderRadius:"12px", borderColor:"grey.500",padding:"0%"}}>

                </ListItem> */}

     );
}
 
export default HomePage;
